OL,3,CThames Water secures #3bn rescue deal
OL,4,Cafter legal challenge dismissed
OL,6,FA group of the utility's secondary
OL,7,Fcreditors, as well as TWUH's parent
OL,8,Fcompany, Thames Water Limited (TWL),
OL,9,Fappealed against the decision at a
OL,10,Fhearing last week.
OL,12,FLiberal Democrat MP Charlie Maynard
OL,13,Falso appealed against the ruling,
OL,14,Fclaiming that the company should
OL,15,Finstead be placed into special
OL,16,Fadministration (SAR) to better serve
OL,17,Fcustomer interests.
