OL,3,CThames Water secures #3bn rescue deal
OL,4,Cafter legal challenge dismissed
OL,6,FIn an order on Monday, Sir Julian
OL,7,FFlaux, sitting with Sir Nicholas
OL,8,FPatten and Lord Justice Zacaroli, said
OL,9,Fthe appeals were dismissed with
OL,10,Freasons to follow in writing "in due
OL,11,Fcourse".
OL,13,FAndrew Thornton KC, for TWL,
OL,14,Fpreviously told the Court of Appeal in
OL,15,Fwritten submissions that the approved
OL,16,Fplan was "designed by senior lenders
OL,17,Ffor the benefit of senior lenders".
OL,19,FHe said that the terms of the plan
OL,20,Fwere "mispriced and inappropriate".
