OL,3,CThames Water secures #3bn rescue deal
OL,4,Cafter legal challenge dismissed
OL,6,FHe continued that the judge, Mr
OL,7,FJustice Leech, "failed to apply the
OL,8,Fcorrect principles" when making his
OL,9,Fdecision to approve the scheme, and
OL,10,Ftherefore "wrongly exercised his
OL,11,Fdiscretion to sanction the plan".
OL,13,FTWUH and its Class A creditors had
OL,14,Fopposed the appeal, with Tom Smith KC,
OL,15,Ffor TWUH, stating in written
OL,16,Fsubmissions that the London court
OL,17,Fshould not interfere with the decision
OL,18,F"unless compelled to do so".
