OL,3,CThames Water secures #3bn rescue deal
OL,4,Cafter legal challenge dismissed
OL,6,FThames Water serves about 16 million
OL,7,Fcustomers ` about 25% of the UK's
OL,8,Fpopulation ` and owns more than 20,000
OL,9,Fmiles of water mains and more than
OL,10,F68,000 miles of sewers across London,
OL,11,Fthe Thames Valley and the Home
OL,12,FCounties.
OL,14,FThe High Court previously heard that
OL,15,Fthe restructuring is intended to be an
OL,16,Finterim measure to keep the utility
OL,17,Frunning before a substantive
OL,18,Frestructuring due later this year.
